# RFC 8288 Link response headers for agent discovery.
# - service-doc → human-readable docs (IANA registered)
# - describedby → /llms.txt machine-readable site summary (IANA registered)
# Applied per-path via Cloudflare Pages' _headers file.

/
  Link: </docs>; rel="service-doc"
  Link: </llms.txt>; rel="describedby"

/docs/*
  Link: </llms.txt>; rel="describedby"
